Soccer Football - Carabao Cup - Semi Final - Second Leg - Tottenham Hotspur v Chelsea - Tottenham Hotspur Stadium, London, Britain - January 12, 2022 Chelsea's Antonio Rudiger celebrates scoring their first goal with Romelu Lukaku 
        
 

